{"tid":1395740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵車廂圖開乘客背包　休班警企圖偷竊罪成上訴駁回","createTime":"2019-08-02T00:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T01:59:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2eaf282cf796dd3415aece020e703091a9c788c","tid":1395740,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190723/s00001/240ac1afe278fad5a328b195bc5322a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190723%2Fs00001%2F240ac1afe278fad5a328b195bc5322a9.jpg&h=2f5579ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n休班男警去年11月被裁定企圖偷竊罪成，今不服定罪及判刑上訴至高院，惟申請遭法官駁回。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n男警去年休班期間乘港鐵時，偷偷拉開尼泊爾裔女乘客的背包拉鏈企圖盜竊，去年11月被裁定企圖偷竊罪成，判監12個月，他今（23日）不服定罪及判刑，上訴至高等法院，但被駁回，法官稍後以書面頒布裁決理由。<br />\n<br />\n代表上訴人梁鴻基的一方指出，梁鴻基案發時在未被截停前已停止偷竊，選擇離開車廂而非繼續偷竊，顯示並無偷竊的動機；至於事主背包拉鏈被打開多少，控方證供存在分歧，顯示證人未必能夠準確判斷梁鴻基有否偷竊行為。<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方反駁，上訴人是否企圖犯案只涉及案情嚴重程度的問題，而案發時證人身處被告右後方位置，距離較近，能夠清楚觀察被告行為。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人去年2月6日在一列由金鐘往尖沙嘴站的港鐵列車第三卡車廂內，打開女事主背包拉鏈。其後在尖沙嘴站被便衣警察截停，之後他自稱是「觀塘伙計」並逃去，警方翌日在觀塘警署外將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190723/s00001/1563858441096/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E5%9C%96%E9%96%8B%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E5%81%B7%E7%AB%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00001%2F1563858441096%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%258C%2585-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%25AB%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=a3fcfe6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00001%2F1563858441096%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%258C%2585-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%25AB%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E&h=952afc4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190723/s00001/1563858441096/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E5%9C%96%E9%96%8B%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%BC%81%E5%9C%96%E5%81%B7%E7%AB%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E</a>"},{"pid":"8188eab0eb9f8a86ae71526eb1a285e87d361b49","tid":1395740,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:23:04.000Z","msg":"召喚戰士一人一信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對黑警加人工! </span></strong></span>黑警你憑咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n記得要改wordings/自由加減!!!幫手推"},{"pid":"796717fe41abd2a681db5aad383500267fd44bb3","tid":1395740,"uid":82532,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:24:25.000Z","msg":"員佐級協會幾時出聲明要個官道歉？"},{"pid":"b9730d6bacdb5ab13b4309ee46b974326f94663b","tid":1395740,"uid":260328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"香港警察 知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bea6bc6aa6c4392b45d5ecbfc42241d685911e","tid":1395740,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:29:13.000Z","msg":"香港法官有撚用咩"},{"pid":"fa24d3f5fddac5784f57e28a4cdaea1991b4733d","